premise_source_doc_sentence: The food balance sheet shows the food items for human consumption , along with how it is produced , used , imported/exported , and how it benefits the society  (  per capita supply  )  .

On the utilization side a distinction is made between the quantities exported , fed to livestock + used for seed , losses during storage and transportation , and food supplies available for human consumption .
